{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"You know, cadaver dissection"},{"time":3000,"text":"is the traditional way of learning human anatomy."},{"time":6000,"text":"For students, it's quite an experience,"},{"time":9000,"text":"but for a school, it could be very difficult"},{"time":12000,"text":"or expensive to maintain."},{"time":15000,"text":"So we learned the majority of anatomic classes taught,"},{"time":19000,"text":"they do not have a cadaver dissection lab."},{"time":23000,"text":"Maybe those reasons, or depending on where you are,"},{"time":27000,"text":"cadavers may not be easily available."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"So to address this, we developed"},{"time":33000,"text":"with a Dr. Brown in Stanford: virtual dissection table."},{"time":37000,"text":"So we call this Anatomage Table."},{"time":42000,"text":"So with this Anatomage Table,"},{"time":45000,"text":"students can experience"},{"time":48000,"text":"the dissection without a human cadaver."},{"time":51000,"text":"And the table form is important,"},{"time":54000,"text":"and since it's touch-interactive,"},{"time":57000,"text":"just like the way they do dissections in the lab,"},{"time":62000,"text":"or furthermore just the way a surgeon operates on a patient"},{"time":66000,"text":"you can literally interact with your table."},{"time":69000,"text":"Our digital body is one-to-one life size,"},{"time":74000,"text":"so this is exactly the way"},{"time":77000,"text":"students will see the real anatomy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"I'm going to"},{"time":83000,"text":"do some demonstrations."},{"time":86000,"text":"As you can see,"},{"time":88000,"text":"I use my finger to interact with my digital body."},{"time":92000,"text":"I'm going to do some cuts."},{"time":95000,"text":"I can cut any way I want to, so I cut right here."},{"time":99000,"text":"Then it's going to show inside."},{"time":103000,"text":"And I can change my cut"},{"time":108000,"text":"to see different parts."},{"time":111000,"text":"Maybe I can cut there,"},{"time":115000,"text":"see the brain,"},{"time":118000,"text":"and I can change my cut."},{"time":121000,"text":"You can see some internal organs."},{"time":124000,"text":"So we call this"},{"time":127000,"text":"the slicer mode."},{"time":138000,"text":"OK, I'm going to do another cut."},{"time":145000,"text":"Right there."},{"time":149000,"text":"This shows a lot of internal structures."},{"time":152000,"text":"So if I want to see the back side,"},{"time":156000,"text":"I can flip"},{"time":159000,"text":"and see from behind."},{"time":162000,"text":"Like this."},{"time":165000,"text":"So if these images are"},{"time":169000,"text":"uncomfortable to you or disturbing to you,"},{"time":173000,"text":"that means we did the right job."},{"time":176000,"text":"So our doctors said"},{"time":179000,"text":"these are eye candies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"So instead of just butchering the body,"},{"time":184000,"text":"I'd like to do more clinically meaningful dissections."},{"time":187000,"text":"What I'm going to do is"},{"time":190000,"text":"I'm going to peel off all the skin, muscles and bones,"},{"time":194000,"text":"just to see a few internal organs."},{"time":197000,"text":"Right here."},{"time":200000,"text":"Let's say I'm going to cut"},{"time":206000,"text":"the liver right here."},{"time":213000,"text":"OK."},{"time":214000,"text":"Let's say I'm interested in looking at the heart."},{"time":217000,"text":"I'm going to do some surgery here."},{"time":221000,"text":"I'm going to cut some veins, arteries."},{"time":225000,"text":"Oops! ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"You don't want to hear \"oops\" in real surgery."},{"time":229000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":231000,"text":"But fortunately, our digital man has \"undo.\""},{"time":234000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":237000,"text":"Okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"All right then."},{"time":250000,"text":"Let me zoom in."},{"time":252000,"text":"I'm going to make a cut right there."},{"time":256000,"text":"And then you can see the inside of the heart."},{"time":262000,"text":"You can see the atrium and the ventricles,"},{"time":265000,"text":"how blood flows to our arteries and veins."},{"time":268000,"text":"Just like this,"},{"time":270000,"text":"students can isolate anybody"},{"time":273000,"text":"and dissect any way you want to."},{"time":275000,"text":"It doesn't have to be always dissection."},{"time":278000,"text":"Since it's digital, we can do reverse dissection."},{"time":281000,"text":"So let me show you,"},{"time":284000,"text":"I'm going to start with the skeletal structure,"},{"time":286000,"text":"and I can add a few internal organs."},{"time":290000,"text":"Yep."},{"time":293000,"text":"Maybe I can add quickly this way."},{"time":300000,"text":"And I can build muscles"},{"time":303000,"text":"gradually,"},{"time":306000,"text":"just like that."},{"time":308000,"text":"We can see tendons and muscles."},{"time":310000,"text":"Wish I could build my muscle this fast."},{"time":314000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":317000,"text":"And this is another way to learn anatomy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"Another thing I can show you is,"},{"time":323000,"text":"more often than not,"},{"time":326000,"text":"doctors get to meet patients"},{"time":328000,"text":"in X-ray form."},{"time":330000,"text":"So,"},{"time":333000,"text":"Anatomage Table shows"},{"time":335000,"text":"exactly how the anatomy will appear in X-ray."},{"time":338000,"text":"You can also interact with your X-ray,"},{"time":342000,"text":"and also if you want,"},{"time":345000,"text":"you can compare"},{"time":347000,"text":"with how anatomy would appear"},{"time":350000,"text":"in X-ray, too."},{"time":352000,"text":"So when you are done,"},{"time":355000,"text":"just bring back the body"},{"time":358000,"text":"and then it's ready for another session."},{"time":362000,"text":"It looks like our table"},{"time":365000,"text":"also can transform gender, too."},{"time":368000,"text":"It's a female now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"So this is Anatomage Table. Thank you."},{"time":373000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}